{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji44","name":"毛泽东全集第44卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/maoquanji44.pdf"],"article":{"title":"给臧克家的信","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"给臧克家“的信"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1961年12月26日）克家同志："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几次惠书，均已收到，甚为感谢。所谈之事，很想谈谈。无耐有些忙，抽不【出】时间来；而且我对于诗的问题，需要加以研究，才有发言权。因此请你等候一些时间吧。专此奉复，敬颂撰安！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九六一年十二月二十六日[1]臧克家，当时任中国作家协会书记处书记、《诗刊》主编。"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1961,"month":12,"day":26}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":502,"page_end":502},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"书信"}]}]}